    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――現在",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、本当にありがとう。まさか、葵の衣装まで\n用意してくれていたとはね。当日の朝、聞いて驚いたわ",
      "startTime": 6.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "貴方のおかげで、四人揃って\nセミファイナルの舞台に立つことが出来た",
      "startTime": 14.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "だから、何も出来ないとか、何も力になれないなんて\nそんなバカなこと、二度と言わないで",
      "startTime": 22.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……はい。もう言いませんよ\nそれにしても約束、本当に果たしちゃいましたね",
      "startTime": 29.2262637485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、貴方をトップアイドルのマネージャーにする\nっていう約束？",
      "startTime": 37.4837188721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4はVENUSプログラムの頂点に立つアイドル\nそういう意味では、約束を果たしたと言えるのかもね",
      "startTime": 43.7205469447,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "でも……考えてみたの。私達にとっての頂点――\nトップアイドルは、ランキング一位に立つこと",
      "startTime": 53.6170550029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "だから、私達LizNoirの\nトップアイドルへの道のりは、まだこれからよ",
      "startTime": 60.3503883362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "今度はサニピや月ストとも戦わないとね。また勝っても\n負けても、貴方を複雑な気分にさせちゃうかしら",
      "startTime": 68.7503863017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはそうなんですけど……勘弁して下さいよ",
      "startTime": 72.7109078405,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、貴方が約束を果たしたと思っているなら……\nそうね、気の利いたプレゼントでも用意すれば？",
      "startTime": 83.0488638242,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　プレゼントですか？　たとえばどんな……？",
      "startTime": 87.1074573356,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "それくらい自分で考えなさい",
      "startTime": 92.2077975749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "大体「何をプレゼントしてほしいんですか」って\n直接聞くような人は、モテないわよ",
      "startTime": 98.328954665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "て、手厳しいですね……分かりました。考えておきます\n……おっと、そろそろ撮影本番ですね",
      "startTime": 106.7666615803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、それじゃ行ってくるわ\nプレゼント、楽しみにしてるわよ",
      "startTime": 113.4057803791,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4478.841814900008,
          "startTime": 117.884622194
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "撮影お疲れ様でした、莉央さん\n相変わらず、手際がいいですね",
      "startTime": 121.4666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "いつも通りよ。それに葵の撮影がもう終わってるから\nスタッフさん達も手慣れているわ。そのおかげよ",
      "startTime": 129.5564595224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "この後、撮影した映像のチェックがあるから\n貴方も付き合ってちょうだい",
      "startTime": 136.5897989592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "おぉ……カッコいい。やっぱり絵になるな\nまるでゲームのラスボスみたいです",
      "startTime": 145.7333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って。それ、アイドルに対する誉め言葉？\n強そうとか、怖いってこと？",
      "startTime": 153.5740847272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いえ、そうじゃなくて、迫力があるというか\n……そうだ！　女王様とか、将軍みたいです",
      "startTime": 161.2666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "……それ、フォローしてるつもりなの？\nまぁいいわ。的外れって訳じゃないし",
      "startTime": 168.7568947476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "実は、衣装デザイナーさんと話し合って決めた\nこの衣装に込めたテーマはね、『戦い』なの",
      "startTime": 176.0235593797,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "いつだったか、さくらに聞かれたわ\n「あなたにとって、アイドルってなんですか？」って",
      "startTime": 183.823572604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio019.m4a",
      "text": "私の答えは……『戦い』だった\n自分の願いを叶えるために、戦いに身を投じる",
      "startTime": 192.3235705694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "そうやって生きていくこと、そのものが\n私にとっては『アイドル』なの",
      "startTime": 199.8235837937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんらしい答えですね。強い覚悟を感じます",
      "startTime": 202.2603816028,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "この衣装は、そんな覚悟を思い出させてくれる\n特別な一着なの",
      "startTime": 211.6580291432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio022.m4a",
      "text": "私達がBIG4に辿り着くまでの道のりは\n険しくて、とても辛いものだったわ",
      "startTime": 217.0247019133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_11_03-rio023.m4a",
      "text": "決勝トーナメントの間、弱い私の気持ちは\n何度も揺らいでしまったけど",
      "startTime": 225.2580382984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
